+# Wire-Memory Integration Quick Start
+# 線協-記憶整合快速開始
+
+This guide provides a quick introduction to the Wire-Memory Integration system.
+
+## Overview
+
+The Wire-Memory Integration combines:
+- **PD_AI Wire Protocol (C)**: Binary wire format for cross-language communication
+- **Memory Quick Mount (Python)**: Particle-based compression and state management
+- **Particle Wire Bridge (Python)**: Bidirectional C/Python conversion layer
+
+## Quick Start
+
+### 1. Compile and Test C Wire Protocol
+
+```bash
+cd particle_core/src/wire
+make test
+```
+
+Expected output:
+```
+✓✓✓ ALL TESTS PASSED ✓✓✓
+Tests run: 8, Tests passed: 8, Tests failed: 0
+```
+
+### 2. Run Python Integration Tests
+
+```bash
+cd /path/to/flow-tasks
+python particle_core/tests/test_wire_memory_integration.py
+```
+
+Expected output:
+```
+✓✓✓ ALL INTEGRATION TESTS PASSED ✓✓✓
+Total tests: 5, Passed: 5, Failed: 0
+```
+
+### 3. Try the CLI
+
+```bash
+# View help
+python particle_core/src/memory/memory_quick_mount.py --help
+
+# Create a test snapshot
+python particle_core/src/memory/memory_quick_mount.py snapshot \
+  --agent test_agent \
+  --state '{"status": "active", "progress": 75}'
+
+# Rehydrate from snapshot
+python particle_core/src/memory/memory_quick_mount.py rehydrate
+```
+
+### 4. Run the Wire Bridge Demo
+
+```bash
+python particle_core/src/memory/particle_wire_bridge.py
+```
+
+## Simple Example
+
+```python
+from particle_wire_bridge import ParticleWireBridge
+
+# Create bridge
+bridge = ParticleWireBridge(use_compression=True)
+
+# Your data
+data = {
+    "agent": "worker-01",
+    "task": "processing",
+    "progress": 75
+}
+
+# Convert to wire format
+wire_data = bridge.python_to_wire(data)
+print(f"Wire size: {len(wire_data)} bytes")
+
+# Convert back to Python
+restored, header = bridge.wire_to_python(wire_data)
+print(f"Restored: {restored}")
+```
+
