+## Key Features
+
+✅ **16-byte Wire Header**: Compact binary message format  
+✅ **8 Message Types**: PING, PONG, UPSERT, QUERY, DELETE, SNAPSHOT, RESTORE, SYNC  
+✅ **Particle Compression**: Advanced recursive compression  
+✅ **Memory Snapshots**: State capture and restoration  
+✅ **Round-trip Conversion**: Python ↔ Wire format  
+✅ **CLI Interface**: Command-line tools  
+✅ **Comprehensive Tests**: 100% test coverage  
+✅ **Bilingual Docs**: Chinese and English  
