+## Troubleshooting
+
+### C compilation fails
+```bash
+# Install build tools
+sudo apt-get install build-essential  # Ubuntu/Debian
+xcode-select --install                # macOS
+```
+
+### Python import errors
+```bash
+# Add to PYTHONPATH
+export PYTHONPATH="${PYTHONPATH}:$(pwd)/particle_core/src/memory"
+```
+
+### Can't find snapshots
+- Check `particle_core/snapshots/` directory
+- Verify `config.yaml` paths are correct
